It really embodied my exact thoughts...that “perfect, untouchable, modern 80s/90s deco Beverly Hills dream house for like a pampered heir.” Jeffree’s pink pastel suit really brought the whole dream together. The room looks like old money / “Daddy’s Money” rich (Paris Hilton, Cher from Clueless, Mary Swanson, and Willy Wonka combined)...so elegant and powerful, yet sweet 🍬✨...Barbie could never. Lol
